# 🌸 Mother's Day Card with Flower Animation

A simple and responsive Mother's Day card that includes a heartfelt message and a beautiful flower animation background.

## Features

- Heartwarming message for Mom
- Flower animation background (from CodePen)
- Ripple-effect button that redirects to a surprise page
- Fully responsive on all devices

## Files

- `index.html` – Main greeting card
- `start1.css` – Styling and animation
- `MothersDay.html` – Surprise page after button click

## Credits

🌼 Flower animation by [Gabi](https://codepen.io/gabrielleee/pen/WNzXjZJ) on CodePen.

---

Happy Mother’s Day! 💐
